sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Suspicious File Creation Activity From Fake Recycle.Bin Folder
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects file write event from/to a fake recycle bin folder that is often used as a staging directory for malware

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Uncommon File Created In Office Startup Folder
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects the creation of a file with an uncommon extension in an Office application startup folder
A General detection for files being created in the Windows startup directory. This could be an indicator of persistence.

threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered ransomware. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.
